# i18n & RTL Standards

- Default locale is `ar` (Arabic). English is `en`.
- Set `dir="rtl"` on `<html>` for Arabic, `dir="ltr"` for English.
- Use logical CSS properties: `ms-*`, `me-*`, `ps-*`, `pe-*`, `start`, `end`.
- Never hardcode left/right for layout — use logical properties.
- All user-facing strings live in `src/messages/{locale}.json`.
- Locale prefix required: `/ar/...` and `/en/...`.
- Language switcher must preserve current page path.
